backend/app/models/equipment_template.py.description: Created 5 new SQLAlchemy models for Equipment Templates feature: ConsultantType (consultant categories), EquipmentTemplate (template definitions with JSONB specs), EquipmentTemplateConsultant (junction table), EquipmentApprovalSubmission (approval tracking), and EquipmentApprovalDecision (decision recording). All models use UUID primary keys, proper timestamps, and CASCADE deletes for parent-child relationships.
